	  in the invert method.

2003-04-29 00:55 +0000 [r1925]  don:

	* set glDrawBuffer( GL_BACK ) in SceneView::draw() when not drawing
	  in stereo mode. Without this, we end up drawing to the wrong
	  buffer when toggling stereo off.

